# English UI Language

- Respond to the user in English.
- Keep all player-facing game text in English (labels, buttons, tooltips, toasts).
- Do not add Chinese UI strings to the Godot game or web build.
- Godot project locale is `en`; web export must pass `locale: 'en'` to `engine.startGame`.
